{"parentUuid":"a4c568da-8063-4bc3-b71f-f8a9e3d8eebf","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"11039e2a-cbed-45eb-accf-f84d3fb4cdfe","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"soft-wobbling-shannon","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011mvQkSEJcxJDEenaGc9zTK","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→\"\"\"\n     2→PCAN-USB MCP Server\n     3→PCANBasic.dll (ctypes) 기반 CAN 통신 서버\n     4→\"\"\"\n     5→import ctypes\n     6→from ctypes import Structure, c_uint32, c_uint8, c_uint16, byref\n     7→import threading\n     8→import time\n     9→from mcp.server.fastmcp import FastMCP\n    10→\n    11→# ── PCAN ctypes 바인딩 ──────────────────────────────────────\n    12→class TPCANMsg(Structure):\n    13→    _fields_ = [\n    14→        (\"ID\", c_uint32),\n    15→        (\"MSGTYPE\", c_uint8),\n    16→        (\"LEN\", c_uint8),\n    17→        (\"DATA\", c_uint8 * 8),\n    18→    ]\n    19→\n    20→class TPCANTimestamp(Structure):\n    21→    _fields_ = [\n    22→        (\"millis\", c_uint32),\n    23→        (\"millis_overflow\", c_uint16),\n    24→        (\"micros\", c_uint16),\n    25→    ]\n    26→\n    27→# 상수\n    28→PCAN_USBBUS1 = 0x51\n    29→PCAN_BAUD_500K = 0x001C\n    30→PCAN_ERROR_OK = 0x00000\n    31→PCAN_ERROR_QRCVEMPTY = 0x00020\n    32→PCAN_MESSAGE_STANDARD = 0x00\n    33→\n    34→# DLL 로드\n    35→try:\n    36→    pcan = ctypes.windll.LoadLibrary(\"PCANBasic.dll\")\n    37→except Exception as e:\n    38→    pcan = None\n    39→    _load_error = str(e)\n    40→\n    41→# ── 상태 관리 ───────────────────────────────────────────────\n    42→_connected = False\n    43→_ign_running = False\n    44→_ign_thread = None\n    45→_tp_running = False\n    46→_tp_thread = None\n    47→_lock = threading.Lock()\n    48→\n    49→# ── 헬퍼 함수 ──────────────────────────────────────────────\n    50→def _send_can(can_id: int, data: list[int]) -> int:\n    51→    \"\"\"CAN 메시지 전송. 성공 시 0 반환.\"\"\"\n    52→    msg = TPCANMsg()\n    53→    msg.ID = can_id\n    54→    msg.MSGTYPE = PCAN_MESSAGE_STANDARD\n    55→    msg.LEN = min(len(data), 8)\n    56→    for i in range(msg.LEN):\n    57→        msg.DATA[i] = data[i] & 0xFF\n    58→    return pcan.CAN_Write(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg))\n    59→\n    60→def _recv_can(timeout_ms: int = 100, filter_ids: list[int] | None = None) -> list[dict]:\n    61→    \"\"\"수신 큐에서 CAN 메시지 읽기. timeout_ms 동안 폴링.\"\"\"\n    62→    results = []\n    63→    msg = TPCANMsg()\n    64→    ts = TPCANTimestamp()\n    65→    deadline = time.monotonic() + timeout_ms / 1000.0\n    66→    while time.monotonic() < deadline:\n    67→        status = pcan.CAN_Read(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg), byref(ts))\n    68→        if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n    69→            can_id = msg.ID\n    70→            if filter_ids and can_id not in filter_ids:\n    71→                continue\n    72→            data = [msg.DATA[i] for i in range(msg.LEN)]\n    73→            results.append({\n    74→                \"id\": f\"0x{can_id:03X}\",\n    75→                \"data\": \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in data),\n    76→                \"raw\": data,\n    77→            })\n    78→        elif status == PCAN_ERROR_QRCVEMPTY:\n    79→            time.sleep(0.001)\n    80→        else:\n    81→            break\n    82→    return results\n    83→\n    84→def _ign_worker():\n    85→    \"\"\"BCM_02 (0x3E0) IGN ON 주기 전송 스레드\"\"\"\n    86→    global _ign_running\n    87→    while _ign_running:\n    88→        _send_can(0x3E0, [0, 0, 0, 0, 0x50, 0x03, 0, 0])\n    89→        time.sleep(0.2)\n    90→\n    91→def _tp_worker():\n    92→    \"\"\"TesterPresent ($3E 80) 주기 전송 스레드\"\"\"\n    93→    global _tp_running\n    94→    while _tp_running:\n    95→        _send_can(0x732, [0x02, 0x3E, 0x80, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00])\n    96→        time.sleep(2.0)\n    97→\n    98→def _parse_heater_status(data: list[int]) -> dict:\n    99→    \"\"\"438h/453h 데이터에서 히터 상태 파싱\"\"\"\n   100→    ht_oper = (data[0] >> 3) & 0xF if len(data) >= 1 else -1\n   101→    mode_map = {2: \"OFF\", 6: \"1단\", 7: \"2단\", 8: \"3단\"}\n   102→    return {\n   103→        \"ht_oper_raw\": ht_oper,\n   104→        \"ht_oper\": mode_map.get(ht_oper, f\"0x{ht_oper:X}\"),\n   105→    }\n   106→\n   107→def _parse_heater_indi(data: list[int]) -> dict:\n   108→    \"\"\"42Eh/42Fh 데이터에서 인디케이터 상태 파싱\"\"\"\n   109→    if len(data) < 3:\n   110→        return {\"error\": \"데이터 부족\"}\n   111→    hi = (data[1] >> 4) & 3\n   112→    mid = (data[1] >> 6) & 3\n   113→    lo = data[2] & 3\n   114→    return {\n   115→        \"3단\": \"ON\" if hi > 0 else \"OFF\",\n   116→        \"2단\": \"ON\" if mid > 0 else \"OFF\",\n   117→        \"1단\": \"ON\" if lo > 0 else \"OFF\",\n   118→    }\n   119→\n   120→def _parse_uds_response(data: list[int]) -> dict:\n   121→    \"\"\"73Ah UDS 응답 파싱\"\"\"\n   122→    if len(data) < 2:\n   123→        return {\"error\": \"데이터 부족\"}\n   124→    sid = data[1]\n   125→    if sid == 0x50:\n   126→        return {\"type\": \"세션전환 OK\", \"session\": data[2] if len(data) > 2 else 0}\n   127→    elif sid == 0x6F:\n   128→        did = f\"F0{data[3]:02X}\" if len(data) > 3 else \"?\"\n   129→        val = data[4] if len(data) > 4 else 0\n   130→        val_map = {0: \"OFF\", 1: \"1단\", 2: \"2단\", 3: \"3단\"}\n   131→        return {\"type\": \"IOControl OK\", \"DID\": did, \"value\": val_map.get(val, f\"0x{val:02X}\")}\n   132→    elif sid == 0x7F:\n   133→        nrc = data[3] if len(data) > 3 else 0\n   134→        nrc_map = {0x22: \"조건미충족\", 0x31: \"범위초과\", 0x33: \"보안접근필요\", 0x7F: \"세션미지원\"}\n   135→        return {\"type\": \"거부\", \"NRC\": nrc_map.get(nrc, f\"0x{nrc:02X}\")}\n   136→    elif sid == 0x7E:\n   137→        return {\"type\": \"TesterPresent OK\"}\n   138→    else:\n   139→        return {\"type\": \"unknown\", \"raw\": \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in data)}\n   140→\n   141→# ── MCP 서버 ────────────────────────────────────────────────\n   142→mcp = FastMCP(\"pcan\", instructions=\"PCAN-USB CAN 통신 서버. 차량 ECU 진단/제어용.\")\n   143→\n   144→@mcp.tool()\n   145→def can_open() -> str:\n   146→    \"\"\"PCAN-USB 접속 (500K baud). 이미 접속 중이면 재접속.\"\"\"\n   147→    global _connected\n   148→    if pcan is None:\n   149→        return f\"PCANBasic.dll 로드 실패: {_load_error}\"\n   150→    # 기존 접속 해제\n   151→    if _connected:\n   152→        pcan.CAN_Uninitialize(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1))\n   153→    status = pcan.CAN_Initialize(\n   154→        c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), c_uint16(PCAN_BAUD_500K), c_uint8(0), c_uint32(0), c_uint16(0)\n   155→    )\n   156→    if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n   157→        _connected = True\n   158→        return \"PCAN-USB 접속 성공 (500K baud)\"\n   159→    else:\n   160→        _connected = False\n   161→        return f\"PCAN-USB 접속 실패 (status=0x{status:X})\"\n   162→\n   163→@mcp.tool()\n   164→def can_close() -> str:\n   165→    \"\"\"PCAN-USB 접속 해제. IGN/TP 전송도 중지.\"\"\"\n   166→    global _connected, _ign_running, _tp_running\n   167→    _ign_running = False\n   168→    _tp_running = False\n   169→    if _connected:\n   170→        pcan.CAN_Uninitialize(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1))\n   171→        _connected = False\n   172→        return \"PCAN-USB 접속 해제\"\n   173→    return \"이미 해제됨\"\n   174→\n   175→@mcp.tool()\n   176→def can_send(can_id: int, data: list[int]) -> str:\n   177→    \"\"\"CAN 메시지 전송.\n   178→    Args:\n   179→        can_id: CAN ID (예: 0x732)\n   180→        data: 데이터 바이트 리스트 (최대 8바이트, 예: [0x02, 0x10, 0x03, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0])\n   181→    \"\"\"\n   182→    if not _connected:\n   183→        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n   184→    status = _send_can(can_id, data)\n   185→    hex_data = \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in data[:8])\n   186→    if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n   187→        return f\"TX OK: 0x{can_id:03X} [{hex_data}]\"\n   188→    return f\"TX 실패 (status=0x{status:X})\"\n   189→\n   190→@mcp.tool()\n   191→def can_recv(timeout_ms: int = 500, filter_ids: list[int] | None = None) -> str:\n   192→    \"\"\"CAN 수신 큐에서 메시지 읽기.\n   193→    Args:\n   194→        timeout_ms: 수신 대기 시간 (밀리초, 기본 500)\n   195→        filter_ids: 수신할 CAN ID 필터 (없으면 전체, 예: [0x438, 0x42E, 0x73A])\n   196→    \"\"\"\n   197→    if not _connected:\n   198→        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n   199→    msgs = _recv_can(timeout_ms, filter_ids)\n   200→    if not msgs:\n   201→        return \"수신 메시지 없음\"\n   202→    lines = []\n   203→    for m in msgs:\n   204→        lines.append(f\"{m['id']}: {m['data']}\")\n   205→    return f\"수신 {len(msgs)}건:\\n\" + \"\\n\".join(lines)\n   206→\n   207→@mcp.tool()\n   208→def can_monitor(can_ids: list[int], duration_ms: int = 3000) -> str:\n   209→    \"\"\"특정 CAN ID를 일정 시간 모니터링하고 변화를 파싱.\n   210→    히터 관련 ID (438h, 42Eh, 453h, 42Fh, 73Ah) 자동 파싱.\n   211→    Args:\n   212→        can_ids: 모니터링할 CAN ID 리스트\n   213→        duration_ms: 모니터링 시간 (밀리초, 기본 3000)\n   214→    \"\"\"\n   215→    if not _connected:\n   216→        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n   217→\n   218→    msg = TPCANMsg()\n   219→    ts = TPCANTimestamp()\n   220→    results = []\n   221→    last_state = {}\n   222→    deadline = time.monotonic() + duration_ms / 1000.0\n   223→\n   224→    while time.monotonic() < deadline:\n   225→        status = pcan.CAN_Read(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg), byref(ts))\n   226→        if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n   227→            can_id = msg.ID\n   228→            if can_id not in can_ids:\n   229→                continue\n   230→            data = [msg.DATA[i] for i in range(msg.LEN)]\n   231→            data_hex = \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in data)\n   232→\n   233→            # 변화 감지\n   234→            key = f\"0x{can_id:03X}\"\n   235→            if key in last_state and last_state[key] == data_hex:\n   236→                continue\n   237→            last_state[key] = data_hex\n   238→\n   239→            # 파싱\n   240→            parsed = \"\"\n   241→            if can_id in (0x438, 0x453):\n   242→                side = \"RL\" if can_id == 0x438 else \"RR\"\n   243→                p = _parse_heater_status(data)\n   244→                parsed = f\" → {side} 히터: {p['ht_oper']}\"\n   245→            elif can_id in (0x42E, 0x42F):\n   246→                side = \"RL\" if can_id == 0x42E else \"RR\"\n   247→                p = _parse_heater_indi(data)\n   248→                parsed = f\" → {side} 인디: 3단={p['3단']} 2단={p['2단']} 1단={p['1단']}\"\n   249→            elif can_id == 0x73A:\n   250→                p = _parse_uds_response(data)\n   251→                parsed = f\" → DIAG: {p}\"\n   252→\n   253→            results.append(f\"{key}: [{data_hex}]{parsed}\")\n   254→        elif status == PCAN_ERROR_QRCVEMPTY:\n   255→            time.sleep(0.001)\n   256→        else:\n   257→            results.append(f\"수신 오류: 0x{status:X}\")\n   258→            break\n   259→\n   260→    if not results:\n   261→        return f\"{duration_ms}ms 동안 변화 없음\"\n   262→    return \"\\n\".join(results)\n   263→\n   264→@mcp.tool()\n   265→def uds_request(data: list[int], timeout_ms: int = 2000) -> str:\n   266→    \"\"\"RLPSU(0x732)에 UDS 요청 전송 후 응답(0x73A) 대기.\n   267→    첫 바이트는 PCI(길이). 자동으로 0x732에 전송하고 0x73A 응답 파싱.\n   268→    Args:\n   269→        data: 전송할 8바이트 (예: [0x02, 0x10, 0x03, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0] = Extended Session)\n   270→        timeout_ms: 응답 대기 시간\n   271→    \"\"\"\n   272→    if not _connected:\n   273→        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n   274→\n   275→    # 수신 큐 비우기\n   276→    msg = TPCANMsg()\n   277→    ts = TPCANTimestamp()\n   278→    while pcan.CAN_Read(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg), byref(ts)) == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n   279→        pass\n   280→\n   281→    # 요청 전송\n   282→    status = _send_can(0x732, data)\n   283→    if status != PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n   284→        return f\"TX 실패 (status=0x{status:X})\"\n   285→\n   286→    hex_data = \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in data[:8])\n   287→    result = f\"TX: 0x732 [{hex_data}]\\n\"\n   288→\n   289→    # 응답 대기\n   290→    deadline = time.monotonic() + timeout_ms / 1000.0\n   291→    while time.monotonic() < deadline:\n   292→        status = pcan.CAN_Read(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg), byref(ts))\n   293→        if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n   294→            if msg.ID == 0x73A:\n   295→                resp_data = [msg.DATA[i] for i in range(msg.LEN)]\n   296→                resp_hex = \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in resp_data)\n   297→                parsed = _parse_uds_response(resp_data)\n   298→                result += f\"RX: 0x73A [{resp_hex}]\\n→ {parsed}\"\n   299→                return result\n   300→        elif status == PCAN_ERROR_QRCVEMPTY:\n   301→            time.sleep(0.001)\n   302→        else:\n   303→            return result + f\"수신 오류: 0x{status:X}\"\n   304→\n   305→    return result + \"응답 없음 (타임아웃)\"\n   306→\n   307→@mcp.tool()\n   308→def ign_start() -> str:\n   309→    \"\"\"BCM_02 (0x3E0) IGN ON 주기 전송 시작 (200ms).\n   310→    ECU가 IGN ON을 인식하도록 BCM_Ign1InSta=1, BCM_Ign2InSta=1 전송.\n   311→    \"\"\"\n   312→    global _ign_running, _ign_thread\n   313→    if not _connected:\n   314→        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n   315→    if _ign_running:\n   316→        return \"이미 전송 중\"\n   317→    _ign_running = True\n   318→    _ign_thread = threading.Thread(target=_ign_worker, daemon=True)\n   319→    _ign_thread.start()\n   320→    return \"IGN ON 전송 시작 (0x3E0, 200ms 주기)\"\n   321→\n   322→@mcp.tool()\n   323→def ign_stop() -> str:\n   324→    \"\"\"IGN ON 주기 전송 중지.\"\"\"\n   325→    global _ign_running\n   326→    _ign_running = False\n   327→    return \"IGN ON 전송 중지\"\n   328→\n   329→@mcp.tool()\n   330→def tp_start() -> str:\n   331→    \"\"\"TesterPresent ($3E 80) 주기 전송 시작 (2초).\n   332→    Extended Session 유지용.\n   333→    \"\"\"\n   334→    global _tp_running, _tp_thread\n   335→    if not _connected:\n   336→        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n   337→    if _tp_running:\n   338→        return \"이미 전송 중\"\n   339→    _tp_running = True\n   340→    _tp_thread = threading.Thread(target=_tp_worker, daemon=True)\n   341→    _tp_thread.start()\n   342→    return \"TesterPresent 전송 시작 (0x732, 2초 주기)\"\n   343→\n   344→@mcp.tool()\n   345→def tp_stop() -> str:\n   346→    \"\"\"TesterPresent 주기 전송 중지.\"\"\"\n   347→    global _tp_running\n   348→    _tp_running = False\n   349→    return \"TesterPresent 전송 중지\"\n   350→\n   351→@mcp.tool()\n   352→def heater_status() -> str:\n   353→    \"\"\"현재 히터 상태 확인. 438h(RL 히터 모드), 42Eh(RL 인디케이터)를 1초간 모니터링.\"\"\"\n   354→    if not _connected:\n   355→        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n   356→\n   357→    msg = TPCANMsg()\n   358→    ts = TPCANTimestamp()\n   359→    ht_status = None\n   360→    ht_indi = None\n   361→    deadline = time.monotonic() + 1.0\n   362→\n   363→    while time.monotonic() < deadline:\n   364→        status = pcan.CAN_Read(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg), byref(ts))\n   365→        if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n   366→            data = [msg.DATA[i] for i in range(msg.LEN)]\n   367→            if msg.ID == 0x438:\n   368→                ht_status = _parse_heater_status(data)\n   369→            elif msg.ID == 0x42E:\n   370→                ht_indi = _parse_heater_indi(data)\n   371→            if ht_status and ht_indi:\n   372→                break\n   373→        elif status == PCAN_ERROR_QRCVEMPTY:\n   374→            time.sleep(0.001)\n   375→\n   376→    lines = []\n   377→    if ht_status:\n   378→        lines.append(f\"438h 히터 모드: {ht_status['ht_oper']} (raw=0x{ht_status['ht_oper_raw']:X})\")\n   379→    else:\n   380→        lines.append(\"438h: 수신 없음\")\n   381→    if ht_indi:\n   382→        lines.append(f\"42Eh 인디: 3단={ht_indi['3단']} 2단={ht_indi['2단']} 1단={ht_indi['1단']}\")\n   383→    else:\n   384→        lines.append(\"42Eh: 수신 없음\")\n   385→    return \"\\n\".join(lines)\n   386→\n   387→if __name__ == \"__main__\":\n   388→    mcp.run(transport=\"stdio\")\n   389→"}]},"uuid":"28e06eb4-f714-46df-ba83-ad281d684b8d","timestamp":"2026-02-20T10:09:35.143Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\mcp-servers\\pcan\\server.py","content":"\"\"\"\nPCAN-USB MCP Server\nPCANBasic.dll (ctypes) 기반 CAN 통신 서버\n\"\"\"\nimport ctypes\nfrom ctypes import Structure, c_uint32, c_uint8, c_uint16, byref\nimport threading\nimport time\nfrom mcp.server.fastmcp import FastMCP\n\n# ── PCAN ctypes 바인딩 ──────────────────────────────────────\nclass TPCANMsg(Structure):\n    _fields_ = [\n        (\"ID\", c_uint32),\n        (\"MSGTYPE\", c_uint8),\n        (\"LEN\", c_uint8),\n        (\"DATA\", c_uint8 * 8),\n    ]\n\nclass TPCANTimestamp(Structure):\n    _fields_ = [\n        (\"millis\", c_uint32),\n        (\"millis_overflow\", c_uint16),\n        (\"micros\", c_uint16),\n    ]\n\n# 상수\nPCAN_USBBUS1 = 0x51\nPCAN_BAUD_500K = 0x001C\nPCAN_ERROR_OK = 0x00000\nPCAN_ERROR_QRCVEMPTY = 0x00020\nPCAN_MESSAGE_STANDARD = 0x00\n\n# DLL 로드\ntry:\n    pcan = ctypes.windll.LoadLibrary(\"PCANBasic.dll\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    pcan = None\n    _load_error = str(e)\n\n# ── 상태 관리 ───────────────────────────────────────────────\n_connected = False\n_ign_running = False\n_ign_thread = None\n_tp_running = False\n_tp_thread = None\n_lock = threading.Lock()\n\n# ── 헬퍼 함수 ──────────────────────────────────────────────\ndef _send_can(can_id: int, data: list[int]) -> int:\n    \"\"\"CAN 메시지 전송. 성공 시 0 반환.\"\"\"\n    msg = TPCANMsg()\n    msg.ID = can_id\n    msg.MSGTYPE = PCAN_MESSAGE_STANDARD\n    msg.LEN = min(len(data), 8)\n    for i in range(msg.LEN):\n        msg.DATA[i] = data[i] & 0xFF\n    return pcan.CAN_Write(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg))\n\ndef _recv_can(timeout_ms: int = 100, filter_ids: list[int] | None = None) -> list[dict]:\n    \"\"\"수신 큐에서 CAN 메시지 읽기. timeout_ms 동안 폴링.\"\"\"\n    results = []\n    msg = TPCANMsg()\n    ts = TPCANTimestamp()\n    deadline = time.monotonic() + timeout_ms / 1000.0\n    while time.monotonic() < deadline:\n        status = pcan.CAN_Read(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg), byref(ts))\n        if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n            can_id = msg.ID\n            if filter_ids and can_id not in filter_ids:\n                continue\n            data = [msg.DATA[i] for i in range(msg.LEN)]\n            results.append({\n                \"id\": f\"0x{can_id:03X}\",\n                \"data\": \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in data),\n                \"raw\": data,\n            })\n        elif status == PCAN_ERROR_QRCVEMPTY:\n            time.sleep(0.001)\n        else:\n            break\n    return results\n\ndef _ign_worker():\n    \"\"\"BCM_02 (0x3E0) IGN ON 주기 전송 스레드\"\"\"\n    global _ign_running\n    while _ign_running:\n        _send_can(0x3E0, [0, 0, 0, 0, 0x50, 0x03, 0, 0])\n        time.sleep(0.2)\n\ndef _tp_worker():\n    \"\"\"TesterPresent ($3E 80) 주기 전송 스레드\"\"\"\n    global _tp_running\n    while _tp_running:\n        _send_can(0x732, [0x02, 0x3E, 0x80, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00])\n        time.sleep(2.0)\n\ndef _parse_heater_status(data: list[int]) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"438h/453h 데이터에서 히터 상태 파싱\"\"\"\n    ht_oper = (data[0] >> 3) & 0xF if len(data) >= 1 else -1\n    mode_map = {2: \"OFF\", 6: \"1단\", 7: \"2단\", 8: \"3단\"}\n    return {\n        \"ht_oper_raw\": ht_oper,\n        \"ht_oper\": mode_map.get(ht_oper, f\"0x{ht_oper:X}\"),\n    }\n\ndef _parse_heater_indi(data: list[int]) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"42Eh/42Fh 데이터에서 인디케이터 상태 파싱\"\"\"\n    if len(data) < 3:\n        return {\"error\": \"데이터 부족\"}\n    hi = (data[1] >> 4) & 3\n    mid = (data[1] >> 6) & 3\n    lo = data[2] & 3\n    return {\n        \"3단\": \"ON\" if hi > 0 else \"OFF\",\n        \"2단\": \"ON\" if mid > 0 else \"OFF\",\n        \"1단\": \"ON\" if lo > 0 else \"OFF\",\n    }\n\ndef _parse_uds_response(data: list[int]) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"73Ah UDS 응답 파싱\"\"\"\n    if len(data) < 2:\n        return {\"error\": \"데이터 부족\"}\n    sid = data[1]\n    if sid == 0x50:\n        return {\"type\": \"세션전환 OK\", \"session\": data[2] if len(data) > 2 else 0}\n    elif sid == 0x6F:\n        did = f\"F0{data[3]:02X}\" if len(data) > 3 else \"?\"\n        val = data[4] if len(data) > 4 else 0\n        val_map = {0: \"OFF\", 1: \"1단\", 2: \"2단\", 3: \"3단\"}\n        return {\"type\": \"IOControl OK\", \"DID\": did, \"value\": val_map.get(val, f\"0x{val:02X}\")}\n    elif sid == 0x7F:\n        nrc = data[3] if len(data) > 3 else 0\n        nrc_map = {0x22: \"조건미충족\", 0x31: \"범위초과\", 0x33: \"보안접근필요\", 0x7F: \"세션미지원\"}\n        return {\"type\": \"거부\", \"NRC\": nrc_map.get(nrc, f\"0x{nrc:02X}\")}\n    elif sid == 0x7E:\n        return {\"type\": \"TesterPresent OK\"}\n    else:\n        return {\"type\": \"unknown\", \"raw\": \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in data)}\n\n# ── MCP 서버 ────────────────────────────────────────────────\nmcp = FastMCP(\"pcan\", instructions=\"PCAN-USB CAN 통신 서버. 차량 ECU 진단/제어용.\")\n\n@mcp.tool()\ndef can_open() -> str:\n    \"\"\"PCAN-USB 접속 (500K baud). 이미 접속 중이면 재접속.\"\"\"\n    global _connected\n    if pcan is None:\n        return f\"PCANBasic.dll 로드 실패: {_load_error}\"\n    # 기존 접속 해제\n    if _connected:\n        pcan.CAN_Uninitialize(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1))\n    status = pcan.CAN_Initialize(\n        c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), c_uint16(PCAN_BAUD_500K), c_uint8(0), c_uint32(0), c_uint16(0)\n    )\n    if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n        _connected = True\n        return \"PCAN-USB 접속 성공 (500K baud)\"\n    else:\n        _connected = False\n        return f\"PCAN-USB 접속 실패 (status=0x{status:X})\"\n\n@mcp.tool()\ndef can_close() -> str:\n    \"\"\"PCAN-USB 접속 해제. IGN/TP 전송도 중지.\"\"\"\n    global _connected, _ign_running, _tp_running\n    _ign_running = False\n    _tp_running = False\n    if _connected:\n        pcan.CAN_Uninitialize(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1))\n        _connected = False\n        return \"PCAN-USB 접속 해제\"\n    return \"이미 해제됨\"\n\n@mcp.tool()\ndef can_send(can_id: int, data: list[int]) -> str:\n    \"\"\"CAN 메시지 전송.\n    Args:\n        can_id: CAN ID (예: 0x732)\n        data: 데이터 바이트 리스트 (최대 8바이트, 예: [0x02, 0x10, 0x03, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0])\n    \"\"\"\n    if not _connected:\n        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n    status = _send_can(can_id, data)\n    hex_data = \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in data[:8])\n    if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n        return f\"TX OK: 0x{can_id:03X} [{hex_data}]\"\n    return f\"TX 실패 (status=0x{status:X})\"\n\n@mcp.tool()\ndef can_recv(timeout_ms: int = 500, filter_ids: list[int] | None = None) -> str:\n    \"\"\"CAN 수신 큐에서 메시지 읽기.\n    Args:\n        timeout_ms: 수신 대기 시간 (밀리초, 기본 500)\n        filter_ids: 수신할 CAN ID 필터 (없으면 전체, 예: [0x438, 0x42E, 0x73A])\n    \"\"\"\n    if not _connected:\n        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n    msgs = _recv_can(timeout_ms, filter_ids)\n    if not msgs:\n        return \"수신 메시지 없음\"\n    lines = []\n    for m in msgs:\n        lines.append(f\"{m['id']}: {m['data']}\")\n    return f\"수신 {len(msgs)}건:\\n\" + \"\\n\".join(lines)\n\n@mcp.tool()\ndef can_monitor(can_ids: list[int], duration_ms: int = 3000) -> str:\n    \"\"\"특정 CAN ID를 일정 시간 모니터링하고 변화를 파싱.\n    히터 관련 ID (438h, 42Eh, 453h, 42Fh, 73Ah) 자동 파싱.\n    Args:\n        can_ids: 모니터링할 CAN ID 리스트\n        duration_ms: 모니터링 시간 (밀리초, 기본 3000)\n    \"\"\"\n    if not _connected:\n        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n\n    msg = TPCANMsg()\n    ts = TPCANTimestamp()\n    results = []\n    last_state = {}\n    deadline = time.monotonic() + duration_ms / 1000.0\n\n    while time.monotonic() < deadline:\n        status = pcan.CAN_Read(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg), byref(ts))\n        if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n            can_id = msg.ID\n            if can_id not in can_ids:\n                continue\n            data = [msg.DATA[i] for i in range(msg.LEN)]\n            data_hex = \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in data)\n\n            # 변화 감지\n            key = f\"0x{can_id:03X}\"\n            if key in last_state and last_state[key] == data_hex:\n                continue\n            last_state[key] = data_hex\n\n            # 파싱\n            parsed = \"\"\n            if can_id in (0x438, 0x453):\n                side = \"RL\" if can_id == 0x438 else \"RR\"\n                p = _parse_heater_status(data)\n                parsed = f\" → {side} 히터: {p['ht_oper']}\"\n            elif can_id in (0x42E, 0x42F):\n                side = \"RL\" if can_id == 0x42E else \"RR\"\n                p = _parse_heater_indi(data)\n                parsed = f\" → {side} 인디: 3단={p['3단']} 2단={p['2단']} 1단={p['1단']}\"\n            elif can_id == 0x73A:\n                p = _parse_uds_response(data)\n                parsed = f\" → DIAG: {p}\"\n\n            results.append(f\"{key}: [{data_hex}]{parsed}\")\n        elif status == PCAN_ERROR_QRCVEMPTY:\n            time.sleep(0.001)\n        else:\n            results.append(f\"수신 오류: 0x{status:X}\")\n            break\n\n    if not results:\n        return f\"{duration_ms}ms 동안 변화 없음\"\n    return \"\\n\".join(results)\n\n@mcp.tool()\ndef uds_request(data: list[int], timeout_ms: int = 2000) -> str:\n    \"\"\"RLPSU(0x732)에 UDS 요청 전송 후 응답(0x73A) 대기.\n    첫 바이트는 PCI(길이). 자동으로 0x732에 전송하고 0x73A 응답 파싱.\n    Args:\n        data: 전송할 8바이트 (예: [0x02, 0x10, 0x03, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0] = Extended Session)\n        timeout_ms: 응답 대기 시간\n    \"\"\"\n    if not _connected:\n        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n\n    # 수신 큐 비우기\n    msg = TPCANMsg()\n    ts = TPCANTimestamp()\n    while pcan.CAN_Read(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg), byref(ts)) == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n        pass\n\n    # 요청 전송\n    status = _send_can(0x732, data)\n    if status != PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n        return f\"TX 실패 (status=0x{status:X})\"\n\n    hex_data = \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in data[:8])\n    result = f\"TX: 0x732 [{hex_data}]\\n\"\n\n    # 응답 대기\n    deadline = time.monotonic() + timeout_ms / 1000.0\n    while time.monotonic() < deadline:\n        status = pcan.CAN_Read(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg), byref(ts))\n        if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n            if msg.ID == 0x73A:\n                resp_data = [msg.DATA[i] for i in range(msg.LEN)]\n                resp_hex = \" \".join(f\"{b:02X}\" for b in resp_data)\n                parsed = _parse_uds_response(resp_data)\n                result += f\"RX: 0x73A [{resp_hex}]\\n→ {parsed}\"\n                return result\n        elif status == PCAN_ERROR_QRCVEMPTY:\n            time.sleep(0.001)\n        else:\n            return result + f\"수신 오류: 0x{status:X}\"\n\n    return result + \"응답 없음 (타임아웃)\"\n\n@mcp.tool()\ndef ign_start() -> str:\n    \"\"\"BCM_02 (0x3E0) IGN ON 주기 전송 시작 (200ms).\n    ECU가 IGN ON을 인식하도록 BCM_Ign1InSta=1, BCM_Ign2InSta=1 전송.\n    \"\"\"\n    global _ign_running, _ign_thread\n    if not _connected:\n        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n    if _ign_running:\n        return \"이미 전송 중\"\n    _ign_running = True\n    _ign_thread = threading.Thread(target=_ign_worker, daemon=True)\n    _ign_thread.start()\n    return \"IGN ON 전송 시작 (0x3E0, 200ms 주기)\"\n\n@mcp.tool()\ndef ign_stop() -> str:\n    \"\"\"IGN ON 주기 전송 중지.\"\"\"\n    global _ign_running\n    _ign_running = False\n    return \"IGN ON 전송 중지\"\n\n@mcp.tool()\ndef tp_start() -> str:\n    \"\"\"TesterPresent ($3E 80) 주기 전송 시작 (2초).\n    Extended Session 유지용.\n    \"\"\"\n    global _tp_running, _tp_thread\n    if not _connected:\n        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n    if _tp_running:\n        return \"이미 전송 중\"\n    _tp_running = True\n    _tp_thread = threading.Thread(target=_tp_worker, daemon=True)\n    _tp_thread.start()\n    return \"TesterPresent 전송 시작 (0x732, 2초 주기)\"\n\n@mcp.tool()\ndef tp_stop() -> str:\n    \"\"\"TesterPresent 주기 전송 중지.\"\"\"\n    global _tp_running\n    _tp_running = False\n    return \"TesterPresent 전송 중지\"\n\n@mcp.tool()\ndef heater_status() -> str:\n    \"\"\"현재 히터 상태 확인. 438h(RL 히터 모드), 42Eh(RL 인디케이터)를 1초간 모니터링.\"\"\"\n    if not _connected:\n        return \"미접속. can_open() 먼저 호출\"\n\n    msg = TPCANMsg()\n    ts = TPCANTimestamp()\n    ht_status = None\n    ht_indi = None\n    deadline = time.monotonic() + 1.0\n\n    while time.monotonic() < deadline:\n        status = pcan.CAN_Read(c_uint16(PCAN_USBBUS1), byref(msg), byref(ts))\n        if status == PCAN_ERROR_OK:\n            data = [msg.DATA[i] for i in range(msg.LEN)]\n            if msg.ID == 0x438:\n                ht_status = _parse_heater_status(data)\n            elif msg.ID == 0x42E:\n                ht_indi = _parse_heater_indi(data)\n            if ht_status and ht_indi:\n                break\n        elif status == PCAN_ERROR_QRCVEMPTY:\n            time.sleep(0.001)\n\n    lines = []\n    if ht_status:\n        lines.append(f\"438h 히터 모드: {ht_status['ht_oper']} (raw=0x{ht_status['ht_oper_raw']:X})\")\n    else:\n        lines.append(\"438h: 수신 없음\")\n    if ht_indi:\n        lines.append(f\"42Eh 인디: 3단={ht_indi['3단']} 2단={ht_indi['2단']} 1단={ht_indi['1단']}\")\n    else:\n        lines.append(\"42Eh: 수신 없음\")\n    return \"\\n\".join(lines)\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    mcp.run(transport=\"stdio\")\n","numLines":389,"startLine":1,"totalLines":389}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"a4c568da-8063-4bc3-b71f-f8a9e3d8eebf"}
{"parentUuid":"28e06eb4-f714-46df-ba83-ad281d684b8d","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"11039e2a-cbed-45eb-accf-f84d3fb4cdfe","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"soft-wobbling-shannon","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01QEM2vYFAsmjW5p5PToMdjR","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the MCP server. Since I don't have MCP tools available directly, I'll write a Python script that reuses the same PCANBasic.dll ctypes approach to perform the full test sequence. The script will:\n\n1. Open PCAN-USB\n2. Start IGN (BCM_02)\n3. Wait 1 second\n4. Enter Extended Session\n5. Start TesterPresent\n6. Send heater 3-step ON → check status (should be 3단)\n7. Wait for ECU to descend to 2단 → check status\n8. Wait for ECU to descend to 1단 → check status\n\n\n9. Send heater OFF → check status\n10. Clean up\n\nThe key insight from the documentation is that once I send the 3-step ON command, the ECU automatically descends through all levels, so I need to monitor and verify each step. I'll write a comprehensive test script that handles the full sequence with proper status checks at each stage.\n\nWriting test script...","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8297,"cache_read_input_tokens":30123,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":8297},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CYK8z3yPtJpc5MPS5TegE","type":"assistant","uuid":"66665b07-d887-4703-ae8b-119bf2e6aac3","timestamp":"2026-02-20T10:09:45.246Z"}
